description: Update a group access control entry you created using CreateTemplateGroupAccessControlEntry.

parameters.name: AccessRights
parameters.description: Allow or deny permissions for an Active Directory group to enroll or autoenroll certificates for a template. AutoEnroll (string) --- Allow or deny an Active Directory group from autoenrolling certificates issued against a template. The Active Directory group must be allowed to enroll to allow autoenrollment Enroll (string) --- Allow or deny an Active Directory group from enrolling certificates issued against a template.

nested_params.name: AutoEnroll
nested_params.description: Allow or deny an Active Directory group from autoenrolling certificates issued against a template. The Active Directory group must be allowed to enroll to allow autoenrollment.

nested_params.name: Enroll
nested_params.description: Allow or deny an Active Directory group from enrolling certificates issued against a template.

parameters.name: GroupSecurityIdentifier
parameters.description: Security identifier (SID) of the group object from Active Directory. The SID starts with 'S-'.

parameters.name: TemplateArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) that was returned when you called CreateTemplate.
